    <item>
      <title>人生的第一篇博文</title>
      <link>http://loveyyh.top/2022/09/14/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%87/</link>
      <guid>http://loveyyh.top/2022/09/14/%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%87/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Sep 2022 12:59:18 GMT</pubDate>
      
        
        
      <description>&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plaintext&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span c</description>
        
      
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">金色的天空有五弦琴</span><br><span class="line">最后的审判将要来临</span><br><span class="line">天空在黯淡</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">他说</span><br><span class="line">汝之命运就此决定</span><br><span class="line">该得到的尚未得到</span><br><span class="line">该丧失的早已丧失</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">弦如强弓，声若惊雷</span><br><span class="line">乌云笼罩着我</span><br><span class="line">正如一张黑色唱片</span><br><span class="line">奏出死亡的和弦</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">得到的终究会丧失</span><br><span class="line">丧失的不如不得到</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这不是我和她的告别</span><br><span class="line">因为我们并没有相见</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">刘备三拜孔明</span><br><span class="line">为何你见也不见</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">梦还是醒了</span><br><span class="line">我透过窗看见前一个宇宙</span><br><span class="line">他们夸赞美好是如何的天才</span><br><span class="line">排比起兴样样高明</span><br><span class="line">我总算看出古雅的手法</span><br><span class="line">差不多表现了你的秀美</span><br><span class="line">所以他们的赞辞无非是预言</span><br><span class="line">我有幸见到了今日的风景</span><br><span class="line">可惜美好终将消逝</span><br><span class="line">不会永远驻定</span><br><span class="line">可悲的后来之人</span><br><span class="line">我提醒</span><br><span class="line">你们还没生</span><br><span class="line">美的夏天已经死 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">收起你的妄想</span><br><span class="line">他说</span><br><span class="line">葬歌还在继续</span><br><span class="line">真的注定</span><br><span class="line">救赎不会来临</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">天空开始消逝，琴弦在悲鸣</span><br><span class="line">原来天空之外是无物</span><br><span class="line">我的心里也曾如此</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">琴瑟和鸣的开始</span><br><span class="line">为何不得善终</span><br><span class="line">没有相爱的你们</span><br><span class="line">为何开始尝试</span><br><span class="line">我</span><br><span class="line">不</span><br><span class="line">相</span><br><span class="line">信</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">天空开始消逝，琴弦在悲鸣</span><br><span class="line">原来天空之外是无物</span><br><span class="line">我的心里也曾如此</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">鸟儿们开始鸣叫</span><br><span class="line">原来我睡在公园的长椅</span><br><span class="line">我的身旁有个无人</span><br><span class="line">你还是不肯来--重逢</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">总是比告别少</span><br><span class="line">少一次</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2022年9月11日 没有新生的黎明中</p><p>下一篇就介绍这首诗，和它的故事吧</p>]]></content:encoded>
      
      
